			<div class="postrow">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Cybernetic Enhancements
				</h2>
				

						
							
							
							
						
						
				<div class="content ">
					<div id="post_message_1769608">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							So, in the future lets assume that we have some tech where we can achieve Ghost in the Shell or Deus Ex level of enhancements, what skill ups are you going for?<br />
<br />
I am going for increased jump so that I can dunk like Lebron James again or someone from NBA Jams.  I think echo location is sweet so I could boost that skill, then I would add the ability to see in infrared, and feel magnetic fields in a precise manner.  I also want the ability to see an overlay of the world with useful info through a HUD (we can already do this to an extent, but I want something awesome).  I would also add additional arms so that I could control more devices simultaneously.  <br />
<br />
I could be rocking rocket launchers in two hands and then doing work or bringing up data with my other two being a John Rambo Übermensch that can do mechanically intensive tasks while simultaneously doing mental work.  I want a neural interface to computers too and the ability to store ever thing I have ever seen and transform that with my mind into a new novel realization instead of having to do so with limited memory, basically utilize our resources well instead of having so much redundant matter in the event of trauma.<br />
<br />
<br />
I also want some wolverine claws and an adamantium skeleton as that is super sweet.  I also wish that I could curl up with a tough exterior armor like an armadillo or turtle,  providing an excellent barrier in the event of overwhelming odds.  I would also like to be able to do complex calculations in real time such that it is effectively the same as recalling from memory
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
			</div>
			
